---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="MOSTY terms of service — conditions for using our website and purchasing products."
>
  <Section background="green" padding="sm">
    <div class="text-center py-4">
      <h1 class="text-h1 text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-white/80">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-text max-w-none prose-headings:font-heading prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:font-bold prose-h2:mt-10 prose-a:text-brand-green">
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using mostytale.com, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.</p>

      <h2>2. Website Use</h2>
      <p>Our website is intended to provide information about MOSTY products and direct you to authorized retailers (primarily Amazon.com). You may use our website for lawful purposes only.</p>

      <h2>3. Product Purchases</h2>
      <p>MOSTY products are sold through Amazon.com. All purchases are subject to Amazon's terms of service, return policies, and shipping policies. We are not responsible for transactions conducted on Amazon's platform.</p>

      <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on mostytale.com — including text, images, logos, and product descriptions — is the intellectual property of MOSTY unless otherwise noted. Unauthorized use or reproduction is prohibited.</p>

      <h2>5. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>While we strive for accuracy, product specifications, pricing, and availability are subject to change. MOSTY is not liable for any damages arising from the use of our website or products.</p>

      <h2>6. Amazon Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>Some links on our website are affiliate links. We may earn a commission when you make a purchase through these links, at no additional cost to you.</p>

      <h2>7. User-Generated Content</h2>
      <p>By submitting content through our contact form or other means, you grant MOSTY a non-exclusive license to use that content for customer service and business purposes.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mostytale.com">support@mostytale.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
